list.item:
Supervisor child - adding the configuration parameter {sup_child, true}
       the oe_create_link/2 function returns {ok, Pid, ObjRef} which
       can be handled by the application supervisor/stdlib-1.7 or later.

desc.p:
If the configuration parameter {{handle_info, "Module::Interface"}, true}
          is passed to IC and process_flag(trap_exit,true) is set in the init() 
          call-back this function must be exported.
